      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## v1.5.0 - i18n + Budget AI Provider\n\n### Full i18n (12 languages)\n- 12 languages with instant UI refresh (no restart needed)\n- English, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Korean, German, French, Russian, Portuguese, Italian, Turkish, Arabic\n- All ~600 UI strings internationalized via t() engine\n- Language selector in Settings with live refresh\n- Spanish translations for all settings, chat, and tools (~437 keys)\n\n### Budget AI Provider (Pro)\n- Bundled managed AI provider via Mistral Nemo (OpenRouter). No API key needed\n- 50 queries/day with server-side tracking (persists across devices)\n- Agent Mode fully supported with native tool calling\n- Usage badge in chat header + budget section in Settings\n- API key NEVER leaves the Cloudflare Worker\n\n### Agent Mode - Same for all providers\n- ToolRouter, PlanTracker, ContextCompactor, anti-loop\n- Mistral Nemo tool calling with auto-find path resolution\n- Hallucinated tools silently skipped\n\n### Tests\n- 15/15 suites passing, 146/146 tests\n- TypeScript strict mode: 0 errors\n\n### Build\n- main.js clean store build: 2.8 MB\n- 48 files changed, 8,132 insertions",
