      "author": "JosefBelzer",
      "description": "🌐 Full English Localization\r\nAll ~156 user-facing strings translated from Spanish to English:\r\n\r\nSystem messages and toasts (new Notice)\r\nSettings UI labels, descriptions, placeholders\r\nHeader badges (🔒 Local/☁️ Cloud, ⭐ Pro/🆓 Free)\r\nAll 14 tool descriptions, parameter descriptions, error/result strings\r\nSlash command prompts (/summarize, /translate, etc.)\r\nExport chat labels (User, Assistant, System)\r\nToolRouter classification prompt now bilingual (English + Spanish examples)\r\n🔒 Security & Compliance\r\nGitHub artifact attestations via .github/workflows/release.yml (Sigstore-powered)\r\nauthorUrl fixed → GitHub profile (not plugin repo)\r\nmain.js minified: 3.86 MB (under 5 MB Obsidian Sync limit)\r\nbuiltin-modules removed from dependencies\r\nCSS !important replaced by higher-specificity selectors\r\nVault enumeration disclosure added to README\r\n🧠 ToolRouter Bilingual\r\nFast-path now handles both create|generate|make|add|populate (English) and crea|genera|crear|añade (Spanish)\r\nLLM classification prompt includes 12 English + 12 Spanish few-shot examples\r\nNo degradation for international users\r\n🧪 Tests\r\n15/15 test suites passing, 146/146 tests ✅\r\nTest assertions updated to match English strings\r\n📦 Build\r\nmain.js clean store build: 3.86 MB\r\nTypeScript strict mode: 0 errors\r\n⏳ Payment Gateway\r\nLemon Squeezy account is pending activation — Pro tier not yet available for purchase\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/JosefBelzer/Copilot-Personal/compare/1.4.2...1.4.3\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/JosefBelzer/Copilot-Personal/compare/1.4.2...1.4.3",
